reviewText: I ordered this for my mom and she loves it!

outrageous pricing when you can get episodes off the internet for free such as youtube.
In some episodes special effect of overlaying was used which IMHO didn't contribute to the scenes. the stories are good.
I had said I was a Perry Mason fan. I guess I should have said, a Raymond Burr fan.

I do not know why I can't get this here in the USA. I bought a player a few years ago so I could get the shows I wanted from other countries. It was worth the money. This is a very good show. The acting is great. The quality of the dvd is very good, so is the sound. The packaging is a little tight. I had a real hard time getting the disks out.

I love Ironside. There is really not much more to say about it. I had to get a different (Zone free) DVD player to watch this and some other seasons. That wasn't as expensive as I thought it would be.
FINALLY ORDERED THIS SET AFTER YEARS OF WAITING FOR IT TO BE RELEASED IN USA....CAN'T BE MORE PLEASED...GREAT QUALITY AND IRONSIDE LOOKS AND SOUNDS GREAT....
